    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been reviewed. Seven factors were formally assessed against ASME V&V 40 level requirements; all seven achieved at least their required level. The remaining six factors were either scoped out or not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 expectations for a Class II device. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the claim that the CFD model can reliably identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device. The decision to Accept is based on the totality of structured factor evidence reviewed by the assessment team.",
